title: BATTLE OF HONOR AND VALOR - Napoleon Total War Gameplay
description:
Napoleon Total War Gameplay - Austria's army, lead by Archduke Charles, march in the deserts of egypt.  Standing in there way is an elite force from Russia.  Why are these two factions fight each other in the desert? I don't know, but it should get a great one!  Enjoy the Battle :D

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
